Kenya's Top Commercial Law Firm Mmc Africa Has Teamed Up With Africa's International Law Firm Asafo & Co To Form Mmc Asafo In Order To Provide A Unique And Intergrated Offering Of Top Tier Legal Services Exclusively Dedicated To The African Continent. The Mmc Asafo Team Is Based In Different Offices, With A Balanced Presence In France And In The Major African Business Hubs Of Nairobi, Abidjan, Casablanca And Jo'burg